data.description: Updated, and in turn-key condition!  Warm and inviting home in desirable Watermill - featuring great amenities and NO CDD FEES! This updated 3/2 split-bedroom plan welcomes you in the foyer, leading to spacious family and dining rooms overlooking the large kitchen with an abundance of counter and cabinet space (and breakfast nook!). Inviting primary bedroom with walk-in shower (2023) in the bathroom. French doors lead out to the huge covered lanai and generous fenced backyard. Roof and HVAC only 4 years old. Other benefits include a full-house gas generator, plantation shutters, tile flooring throughout, irrigation sys, water softener, alarm sys, termite bond. Watermill amenities feature pools, playground, tennis/volleyball/basketball courts. Conveniently located near Oakleaf Town Center!
